---
title: Beef & Spinach Cottage Pie with Parmesan Mash
description: This cosy dinner packs a flavourful punch, with a veggie-loaded beef base and a creamy Parmesan mash topping. Give the dish a final touch by placing it under the grill till toasty brown and perfectly delicious!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5cd3b0d4afe67400136c8703-7d574a10.jpg
